First Department,

September, 1977

(September 15, 1977) Nautec Leasing Corp., Appellant, v Chester, Inc., Respondent.

After preargument conference, appeal from order of the Supreme Court, New York County, entered on March 21, 1977, and from the judgment of said court entered on March 29, 1977, withdrawn, with prejudice and without costs as to either party. Murphy, P. J.
